---
// Astro component script section
---

<section id="music" class="bg-black text-white py-24 px-4" data-name="music-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-16 text-center">MUSIC</h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            {/* Description Column */}
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-light mb-4">Our Setlist</h3>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6">
                    Journey with us through Coldplay's legendary first three albums - Parachutes, 
                    A Rush of Blood to the Head, and X&Y. These albums defined an era and 
                    established Coldplay as one of the world's greatest bands.
                </p>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-300">
                    From the raw intimacy of "Yellow" and "Trouble", through the epic soundscapes 
                    of "The Scientist" and "Clocks", to the electronic-infused "Talk" and "Speed 
                    of Sound" - our 90-minute show captures the essence of Coldplay's most 
                    influential period.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-8">
                    <a 
                        href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/7CyaG99gCDiKnFT85zytZe" 
                        target="_blank" 
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="inline-block border-2 border-white px-8 py-3 hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-colors"
                    >
                        Open in Spotify
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            {/* Spotify Embed Column */}
            <div class="h-[600px] bg-black/50 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                <iframe 
                    src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/playlist/7CyaG99gCDiKnFT85zytZe?utm_source=generator" 
                    width="100%" 
                    height="100%" 
                    frameborder="0" 
                    allowfullscreen="" 
                    allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" 
                    loading="lazy"
                    class="w-full h-full"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section> 